com.impinj.octane

Class FeatureSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.impinj.octane.FeatureSet

  • public class FeatureSet
extends java.lang.Object
    The FeatureSet class holds the capabilities and features of an Impinj reader. You can query the feature set from the ImpinjReader class.
    See Also:
    ImpinjReader.queryFeatureSet()
